snippet.title: Best VGM 861 - Castlevania : Lords of Shadow - Waterfalls of Agharta
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1344 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0fvt7_n9CU

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3
Castlevania : Lords of Shadow (2009)
Waterfalls of Agharta
Oscar Araujo
